- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as linear logic has applications in programming language semantics.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as linear logic has been used in some areas of AI, such as natural language processing.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is the least likely category as the paper does not deal with data structures or algorithms.
